room_title: Escape room "The Temple" by Chambers Escape Games in Honolulu
room_description: You are a team of treasure hunters, aiming to break into an ancient Egyptian temple to steal the relics within. Your man on the outside has bought you 60 minutes before the authorities come and close the site down for good â€“ so you have this small window of time to break in, steal the Pharaoh's Golden Idol (if it even exists...) and get out. Be warned: There are rumors of ancient traps and curses that lay within, protecting against tomb raiders. But of course, you don't believe in any of that nonsense...
